{"version":"NotebookV1","origId":3782449879829374,"name":"S3_Qualite_Stream_LFA","language":"python","commands":[{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646125,"guid":"adb7175e-e935-4734-b73d-2b90623a9d7a","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":2.0,"command":"%md\n# S3 — Qualité en flux et détection d'anomalies\n\n**Auteur** : Lorenzo Faloci — trigramme `LFA`\n**Cours** : Spark Structured Streaming — Séance 3\n**Date** : 2026-05-19\n\n## Objectif\n\nÀ partir de `silver_stream_taxi` (alimentée par S2), produire deux tables\nDelta distinctes via routage par `quality_flag` :\n\n- **`gold_stream_taxi`** : lignes valides\n- **`quarantine_stream_taxi`** : lignes rejetées\n\nLe pipeline **ne doit jamais crasher** sur donnée corrompue : routage\nvia `when/otherwise`, jamais d'exception levée.\n\n## Paramètre imposé\n\n- Simulateur : **`mode=\"chaos\"`** + **`chaos_ratio=0.20`** → 20% des\n  trajets injectent une corruption parmi 6 types.\n\n## Critères de rejet\n\n| quality_flag | Condition | Source corruption |\n|---|---|---|\n| `MONTANT_NEGATIF` | `total_amount < 0` ou `fare_amount < 0` | `_negative_amount` |\n| `DISTANCE_NULLE` | `trip_distance <= 0` | `_zero_distance` |\n| `DISTANCE_ABERRANTE` | `trip_distance > 100` (miles) | `_impossible_distance` (9999) |\n| `LOCATION_NULLE` | `PULocationID IS NULL` | `_null_location` |\n| `INVERSION_TEMPS` | `dropoff < pickup` | `_inverted_timestamps` (bonus, non couvert par flags standards) |\n| `ANOMALIE_STATISTIQUE` | `\\|z_score(total_amount)\\| > 3` | `_huge_amount` (z-score sur montant) |\n| `VALIDE` | aucune des conditions ci-dessus | — |\n\nNote : `_impossible_distance` (9999 miles) n'aurait pas été capturé\npar `ANOMALIE_STATISTIQUE` car le z-score porte sur `total_amount`, pas\nsur `trip_distance`. On ajoute donc un seuil dédié à 100 miles (au-delà,\nc'est physiquement impossible pour un trajet taxi intra-NYC, même\nvers les aéroports de banlieue).\n\nLe **z-score** est calculé par borough via Stream-Static Join avec une\ntable batch de référence (`ref_borough_stats`). Si le borough est null\nou absent de la référence, on **renvoie VALIDE** (pas d'anomalie\nstatistique inférable, on évite les `NaN` qui invalideraient le flag).","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":null,"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":null,"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"47e951cc-2192-437c-a8cf-e619e78c6168"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646126,"guid":"d07da821-3189-4606-9903-da6209402fbf","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":3.0,"command":"%md\n## 1. Paramètres","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":null,"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":null,"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"13e67e46-6115-405b-9595-f82b6e69c298"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646127,"guid":"17f5375d-b953-456c-8949-fd7b0bd666b9","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":4.0,"command":"TRIGRAMME = \"LFA\"\nCATALOG = \"workspace\"\nSCHEMA  = f\"tp_spark_{TRIGRAMME.lower()}\"\n\n# Volumes UC (créés en S1/S2, idempotent)\nVOL_SCRIPTS     = f\"/Volumes/{CATALOG}/{SCHEMA}/scripts\"\nVOL_RAW_DATA    = f\"/Volumes/{CATALOG}/{SCHEMA}/raw_data\"\nVOL_CHECKPOINTS = f\"/Volumes/{CATALOG}/{SCHEMA}/checkpoints\"\nVOL_SCHEMAS     = f\"/Volumes/{CATALOG}/{SCHEMA}/schemas\"\n\n# Chemins applicatifs\nSIM_OUTPUT_PATH        = f\"{VOL_RAW_DATA}/stream_input/\"\nCHECKPOINT_BRONZE      = f\"{VOL_CHECKPOINTS}/bronze_stream/\"\nCHECKPOINT_SILVER      = f\"{VOL_CHECKPOINTS}/silver_stream/\"\nCHECKPOINT_GOLD        = f\"{VOL_CHECKPOINTS}/gold_stream/\"\nCHECKPOINT_QUARANTINE  = f\"{VOL_CHECKPOINTS}/quarantine_stream/\"\nSCHEMA_LOC_BRONZE      = f\"{VOL_SCHEMAS}/bronze_stream/\"\n\n# Tables\nBRONZE_STREAM_TABLE    = f\"{CATALOG}.{SCHEMA}.bronze_stream_taxi\"\nSILVER_STREAM_TABLE    = f\"{CATALOG}.{SCHEMA}.silver_stream_taxi\"\nGOLD_STREAM_TABLE      = f\"{CATALOG}.{SCHEMA}.gold_stream_taxi\"\nQUARANTINE_TABLE       = f\"{CATALOG}.{SCHEMA}.quarantine_stream_taxi\"\nREF_ZONES_TABLE        = f\"{CATALOG}.{SCHEMA}.ref_taxi_zones\"\nREF_BOROUGH_STATS      = f\"{CATALOG}.{SCHEMA}.ref_borough_stats\"\n\nprint(f\"GOLD       = {GOLD_STREAM_TABLE}\")\nprint(f\"QUARANTINE = {QUARANTINE_TABLE}\")","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":{"type":"listResults","data":[{"type":"ansi","data":"GOLD       = workspace.tp_spark_lfa.gold_stream_taxi\nQUARANTINE = workspace.tp_spark_lfa.quarantine_stream_taxi\n","name":"stdout","arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[],"metadata":{}}],"arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[],"metadata":{"isDbfsCommandResult":false}},"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":1779197290491,"submitTime":1779197286844,"finishTime":1779197291552,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":[["ansi",112]],"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"8bec4ec7-a2ac-477f-b8cf-5a89c41f4f8c"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646128,"guid":"29b0580f-a966-49b3-8f95-8f2ec887df3f","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":5.0,"command":"%md\n## 2. Bootstrap idempotent + reset checkpoints S3\n\nSchema + volumes existent déjà (S1/S2). On crée juste les checkpoints\nGold/Quarantaine et on reset les tables S3 pour repartir propre (le test\nde résilience suppose un état initial connu).","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":null,"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":null,"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"fab389ea-bce1-4c51-9059-307b8536c97b"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646129,"guid":"f8b6a9bf-35fa-4b16-b30b-341b832fa3fa","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":6.0,"command":"spark.sql(f\"CREATE SCHEMA IF NOT EXISTS {CATALOG}.{SCHEMA}\")\nfor vol_name in (\"scripts\", \"raw_data\", \"checkpoints\", \"schemas\"):\n    spark.sql(f\"CREATE VOLUME IF NOT EXISTS {CATALOG}.{SCHEMA}.{vol_name}\")\n\ndbutils.fs.mkdirs(SIM_OUTPUT_PATH)\ndbutils.fs.mkdirs(CHECKPOINT_BRONZE)\ndbutils.fs.mkdirs(CHECKPOINT_SILVER)\ndbutils.fs.mkdirs(CHECKPOINT_GOLD)\ndbutils.fs.mkdirs(CHECKPOINT_QUARANTINE)\ndbutils.fs.mkdirs(SCHEMA_LOC_BRONZE)\n\n# Reset Gold/Quarantine pour démarrer S3 propre (tests résilience valides).\n# Bronze + Silver sont conservés (continuent à recevoir les nouveaux trajets).\nfor tbl in (GOLD_STREAM_TABLE, QUARANTINE_TABLE):\n    spark.sql(f\"DROP TABLE IF EXISTS {tbl}\")\nfor cp in (CHECKPOINT_GOLD, CHECKPOINT_QUARANTINE):\n    try:\n        dbutils.fs.rm(cp, recurse=True)\n    except Exception:\n        pass\n    dbutils.fs.mkdirs(cp)\n\nprint(\"OK : checkpoints Gold + Quarantine reset, tables S3 vidées.\")","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":{"type":"listResults","data":[{"type":"ansi","data":"OK : checkpoints Gold + Quarantine reset, tables S3 vidées.\n","name":"stdout","arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[],"metadata":{}}],"arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[],"metadata":{"isDbfsCommandResult":false}},"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":1779197292410,"submitTime":1779197286857,"finishTime":1779197330864,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":[["ansi",60]],"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"6ab2b6d0-88bb-49bb-b3a6-a10f99cfc590"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646130,"guid":"c871b918-4b01-49fd-82cc-f3fbbebbd30e","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":7.0,"command":"%md\n## 3. Table de référence batch — stats par borough\n\nLe PDF mentionne \"votre table Gold de Spark Core S3 pour les stats par\nborough\". Comme la table Spark Core n'est pas disponible côté\n`tp_spark_lfa`, on **calcule les stats à partir de `silver_stream_taxi`**\nen lecture batch (snapshot à l'instant T). C'est une approximation\nraisonnable : `silver_stream_taxi` contient les trajets propres de S2.\n\nOn filtre les valeurs aberrantes (montants négatifs / extrêmes) **avant**\nde calculer les stats, pour ne pas que les corruptions du chaos polluent\nla référence. Cette logique est cohérente avec ce que ferait un job\nbatch Spark Core de référence.","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":null,"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":null,"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"35e255e6-1d4c-4707-823d-4c4022725183"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646131,"guid":"435d12bf-0804-4e45-8a89-2ea8d441cbf4","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":8.0,"command":"from pyspark.sql.functions import avg, stddev, col, count\n\ndf_silver_snapshot = spark.table(SILVER_STREAM_TABLE).filter(\n    (col(\"total_amount\") > 0) &           # exclut MONTANT_NEGATIF\n    (col(\"total_amount\") < 500) &          # exclut MONTANT_ABERRANT\n    (col(\"trip_distance\") > 0) &           # exclut DISTANCE_NULLE\n    (col(\"trip_distance\") < 100) &         # exclut DISTANCE_IMPOSSIBLE\n    col(\"pickup_borough\").isNotNull()\n)\n\nref_stats = (\n    df_silver_snapshot\n        .groupBy(\"pickup_borough\")\n        .agg(\n            avg(\"total_amount\").alias(\"mean_total\"),\n            stddev(\"total_amount\").alias(\"std_total\"),\n            count(\"*\").alias(\"n_samples\"),\n        )\n)\n\n# Sauvegarder en Delta pour le Stream-Static Join\nref_stats.write.format(\"delta\").mode(\"overwrite\").saveAsTable(REF_BOROUGH_STATS)\n\nprint(f\"✓ Table {REF_BOROUGH_STATS} créée.\")\nspark.table(REF_BOROUGH_STATS).show(10, truncate=False)","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":{"type":"listResults","data":[{"type":"ansi","data":"✓ Table workspace.tp_spark_lfa.ref_borough_stats créée.\n+--------------+------------------+------------------+---------+\n|pickup_borough|mean_total        |std_total         |n_samples|\n+--------------+------------------+------------------+---------+\n|Bronx         |21.40518987341773 |11.16967068595653 |79       |\n|Brooklyn      |17.23327272727273 |8.831508864515735 |110      |\n|Manhattan     |17.156761133603233|9.713185285637836 |494      |\n|Queens        |17.117892720306514|10.283630670782678|261      |\n+--------------+------------------+------------------+---------+\n\n","name":"stdout","arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[],"metadata":{}}],"arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[{"name":"df_silver_snapshot","typeStr":"pyspark.sql.connect.dataframe.DataFrame","schema":{"fields":[{"metadata":{},"name":"VendorID","nullable":true,"type":"integer"},{"metadata":{"spark.watermarkDelayMs":300000},"name":"tpep_pickup_datetime","nullable":true,"type":"timestamp"},{"metadata":{},"name":"tpep_dropoff_datetime","nullable":true,"type":"timestamp"},{"metadata":{},"name":"passenger_count","nullable":true,"type":"double"},{"metadata":{},"name":"trip_distance","nullable":true,"type":"double"},{"metadata":{},"name":"PULocationID","nullable":true,"type":"integer"},{"metadata":{},"name":"DOLocationID","nullable":true,"type":"integer"},{"metadata":{},"name":"payment_type","nullable":true,"type":"integer"},{"metadata":{},"name":"fare_amount","nullable":true,"type":"double"},{"metadata":{},"name":"tip_amount","nullable":true,"type":"double"},{"metadata":{},"name":"total_amount","nullable":true,"type":"double"},{"metadata":{},"name":"sim_is_corrupted","nullable":true,"type":"boolean"},{"metadata":{},"name":"sim_batch_id","nullable":true,"type":"integer"},{"metadata":{},"name":"_rescued_data","nullable":true,"type":"string"},{"metadata":{},"name":"ingestion_timestamp","nullable":true,"type":"timestamp"},{"metadata":{},"name":"source_file","nullable":true,"type":"string"},{"metadata":{},"name":"pickup_borough","nullable":true,"type":"string"},{"metadata":{},"name":"pickup_zone","nullable":true,"type":"string"}],"type":"struct"},"tableIdentifier":null},{"name":"ref_stats","typeStr":"pyspark.sql.connect.dataframe.DataFrame","schema":{"fields":[{"metadata":{},"name":"pickup_borough","nullable":true,"type":"string"},{"metadata":{},"name":"mean_total","nullable":true,"type":"double"},{"metadata":{},"name":"std_total","nullable":true,"type":"double"},{"metadata":{},"name":"n_samples","nullable":false,"type":"long"}],"type":"struct"},"tableIdentifier":null}],"metadata":{"isDbfsCommandResult":false}},"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":1779197330881,"submitTime":1779197286869,"finishTime":1779197348182,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":[["ansi",577]],"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"bc7af14e-f379-4748-9af0-cd368c68da72"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646132,"guid":"76c437df-9dc2-4193-bd63-783e3987e42c","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":9.0,"command":"%md\n## 4. Pipeline qualité — routage via `when/otherwise`\n\n### Approche correcte (PDF §1)\n\n> Ajouter une colonne de flag via des conditions `when/otherwise` sur le\n> DataFrame, puis filtrer en deux DataFrames distincts (valide et\n> quarantaine). **Aucune exception n'est levée** : chaque ligne est\n> simplement routée.\n\n### Gestion du z-score et des nulls\n\nLe z-score `(total - mean) / std` produit `NaN` si :\n- `pickup_borough` est null (pas de match dans `ref_borough_stats`)\n- `std_total` est null ou 0 (borough avec un seul échantillon)\n\nOn gère ces cas en **renvoyant VALIDE** quand le z-score n'est pas\ncalculable. C'est plus prudent que de rejeter par défaut (on garde la\ndonnée brute, l'analyste pourra la qualifier plus tard).\n\n### Ordre d'évaluation des `when`\n\nLes conditions sont évaluées **dans l'ordre** : la première qui matche\nl'emporte. On met les anomalies évidentes (MONTANT_NEGATIF,\nDISTANCE_NULLE...) en premier, l'ANOMALIE_STATISTIQUE en dernier. Un\ntrajet à -50$ ET avec un z-score élevé sera classé MONTANT_NEGATIF (plus\nprécis pour l'analyse de causes).","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":null,"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":null,"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"d9e3123b-6d82-4383-977f-cd643797c63e"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646133,"guid":"1fabbcd0-e2b2-4ad4-aa4d-bac67fbfe244","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":10.0,"command":"from pyspark.sql.functions import (\n    col, when, lit, broadcast, abs as F_abs, isnan, isnull\n)\n\nWATERMARK = \"5 minutes\"\n\ndef build_silver_with_quality():\n    \"\"\"Stream Silver enrichi de la colonne quality_flag.\"\"\"\n    df_silver = (\n        spark.readStream\n            .table(SILVER_STREAM_TABLE)\n            .withColumn(\"tpep_pickup_datetime\",\n                        col(\"tpep_pickup_datetime\").cast(\"timestamp\"))\n            .withColumn(\"tpep_dropoff_datetime\",\n                        col(\"tpep_dropoff_datetime\").cast(\"timestamp\"))\n            .withWatermark(\"tpep_pickup_datetime\", WATERMARK)\n    )\n\n    df_stats = spark.table(REF_BOROUGH_STATS).select(\n        col(\"pickup_borough\").alias(\"borough_join\"),\n        col(\"mean_total\"),\n        col(\"std_total\"),\n    )\n\n    df_with_stats = df_silver.join(\n        broadcast(df_stats),\n        df_silver.pickup_borough == df_stats.borough_join,\n        \"left\",\n    ).drop(\"borough_join\")\n\n    # z-score sécurisé : NaN/null si std absent ou nul → renvoyer 0 pour ne\n    # pas déclencher d'ANOMALIE_STATISTIQUE.\n    df_with_z = df_with_stats.withColumn(\n        \"z_score\",\n        when(\n            col(\"std_total\").isNotNull() & (col(\"std_total\") > 0),\n            (col(\"total_amount\") - col(\"mean_total\")) / col(\"std_total\"),\n        ).otherwise(lit(0.0))\n    )\n\n    df_flagged = df_with_z.withColumn(\n        \"quality_flag\",\n        when(col(\"total_amount\") < 0, \"MONTANT_NEGATIF\")\n        .when(col(\"fare_amount\") < 0, \"MONTANT_NEGATIF\")\n        .when((col(\"trip_distance\").isNull()) | (col(\"trip_distance\") <= 0), \"DISTANCE_NULLE\")\n        .when(col(\"trip_distance\") > 100, \"DISTANCE_ABERRANTE\")\n        .when(col(\"PULocationID\").isNull(), \"LOCATION_NULLE\")\n        .when(col(\"tpep_dropoff_datetime\") < col(\"tpep_pickup_datetime\"), \"INVERSION_TEMPS\")\n        .when(F_abs(col(\"z_score\")) > 3, \"ANOMALIE_STATISTIQUE\")\n        .otherwise(\"VALIDE\")\n    )\n\n    return df_flagged\n\n# Sanity check : afficher le schéma\ndf_test = build_silver_with_quality()\ndf_test.printSchema()","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":{"type":"listResults","data":[{"type":"ansi","data":"root\n |-- VendorID: integer (nullable = true)\n |-- tpep_pickup_datetime: timestamp (nullable = true)\n |-- tpep_dropoff_datetime: timestamp (nullable = true)\n |-- passenger_count: double (nullable = true)\n |-- trip_distance: double (nullable = true)\n |-- PULocationID: integer (nullable = true)\n |-- DOLocationID: integer (nullable = true)\n |-- payment_type: integer (nullable = true)\n |-- fare_amount: double (nullable = true)\n |-- tip_amount: double (nullable = true)\n |-- total_amount: double (nullable = true)\n |-- sim_is_corrupted: boolean (nullable = true)\n |-- sim_batch_id: integer (nullable = true)\n |-- _rescued_data: string (nullable = true)\n |-- ingestion_timestamp: timestamp (nullable = true)\n |-- source_file: string (nullable = true)\n |-- pickup_borough: string (nullable = true)\n |-- pickup_zone: string (nullable = true)\n |-- mean_total: double (nullable = true)\n |-- std_total: double (nullable = true)\n |-- z_score: double (nullable = true)\n |-- quality_flag: string (nullable = false)\n\n","name":"stdout","arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[],"metadata":{}}],"arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[{"name":"df_test","typeStr":"pyspark.sql.connect.dataframe.DataFrame","schema":{"fields":[{"metadata":{},"name":"VendorID","nullable":true,"type":"integer"},{"metadata":{"spark.watermarkDelayMs":300000},"name":"tpep_pickup_datetime","nullable":true,"type":"timestamp"},{"metadata":{},"name":"tpep_dropoff_datetime","nullable":true,"type":"timestamp"},{"metadata":{},"name":"passenger_count","nullable":true,"type":"double"},{"metadata":{},"name":"trip_distance","nullable":true,"type":"double"},{"metadata":{},"name":"PULocationID","nullable":true,"type":"integer"},{"metadata":{},"name":"DOLocationID","nullable":true,"type":"integer"},{"metadata":{},"name":"payment_type","nullable":true,"type":"integer"},{"metadata":{},"name":"fare_amount","nullable":true,"type":"double"},{"metadata":{},"name":"tip_amount","nullable":true,"type":"double"},{"metadata":{},"name":"total_amount","nullable":true,"type":"double"},{"metadata":{},"name":"sim_is_corrupted","nullable":true,"type":"boolean"},{"metadata":{},"name":"sim_batch_id","nullable":true,"type":"integer"},{"metadata":{},"name":"_rescued_data","nullable":true,"type":"string"},{"metadata":{},"name":"ingestion_timestamp","nullable":true,"type":"timestamp"},{"metadata":{},"name":"source_file","nullable":true,"type":"string"},{"metadata":{},"name":"pickup_borough","nullable":true,"type":"string"},{"metadata":{},"name":"pickup_zone","nullable":true,"type":"string"},{"metadata":{},"name":"mean_total","nullable":true,"type":"double"},{"metadata":{},"name":"std_total","nullable":true,"type":"double"},{"metadata":{},"name":"z_score","nullable":true,"type":"double"},{"metadata":{},"name":"quality_flag","nullable":false,"type":"string"}],"type":"struct"},"tableIdentifier":null}],"metadata":{"isDbfsCommandResult":false}},"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":1779197348219,"submitTime":1779197286880,"finishTime":1779197349786,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":[["ansi",1006]],"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"ce185787-c38c-43aa-9141-1f1a249f2061"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646134,"guid":"09cbe7aa-47b3-4b0f-a9ef-4c7110a60ff2","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":11.0,"command":"%md\n## 5. Boucle simulateur chaos + 2 jobs (Gold + Quarantaine)\n\n### Configuration simulateur\n\n- `mode=\"chaos\"` + `chaos_ratio=0.20` → 20% de corruptions injectées\n- `rate=20` (cohérent avec S1/S2)\n- `duration_batches=1` (un batch par itération)\n- `seed=200+i` (offset par rapport à S1/S2 pour variété)\n\n### Architecture des jobs\n\nChaque itération de la boucle externe :\n1. Simulateur → fichier Parquet\n2. Job Bronze (lit Parquet) → `bronze_stream_taxi`\n3. Job Silver (lit Bronze) → `silver_stream_taxi`\n4. Job Gold (lit Silver, filtre `quality_flag = VALIDE`) → `gold_stream_taxi`\n5. Job Quarantaine (lit Silver, filtre `quality_flag != VALIDE`) → `quarantine_stream_taxi`\n\n**2 checkpoints distincts** pour Gold et Quarantaine (règle PDF).","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":null,"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":null,"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"a937a549-bbd7-45ca-b3bb-40574a21cc5c"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646135,"guid":"11f3d40d-5e34-480b-b91f-b49a69a75322","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":12.0,"command":"import sys, time, threading\nif VOL_SCRIPTS not in sys.path:\n    sys.path.insert(0, VOL_SCRIPTS)\n\nfrom taxi_simulator import TaxiStreamSimulator\nfrom pyspark.sql.functions import current_timestamp, col\n\ndef build_bronze_stream():\n    \"\"\"Job Bronze (Auto Loader cloudFiles).\"\"\"\n    return (\n        spark.readStream\n            .format(\"cloudFiles\")\n            .option(\"cloudFiles.format\", \"parquet\")\n            .option(\"cloudFiles.schemaLocation\", SCHEMA_LOC_BRONZE)\n            .option(\"cloudFiles.inferColumnTypes\", \"true\")\n            .load(SIM_OUTPUT_PATH)\n            .withColumn(\"ingestion_timestamp\", current_timestamp())\n            .withColumn(\"source_file\", col(\"_metadata.file_path\"))\n    )\n\ndef build_silver_stream():\n    \"\"\"Job Silver (typage + watermark + Stream-Static Join zones).\"\"\"\n    from pyspark.sql.functions import broadcast\n    df_bronze = (\n        spark.readStream\n            .table(BRONZE_STREAM_TABLE)\n            .withColumn(\"tpep_pickup_datetime\",\n                        col(\"tpep_pickup_datetime\").cast(\"timestamp\"))\n            .withColumn(\"tpep_dropoff_datetime\",\n                        col(\"tpep_dropoff_datetime\").cast(\"timestamp\"))\n            .withWatermark(\"tpep_pickup_datetime\", WATERMARK)\n    )\n    df_zones = spark.table(REF_ZONES_TABLE).select(\n        col(\"LocationID\").alias(\"PULocationID_join\"),\n        col(\"Borough\").alias(\"pickup_borough\"),\n        col(\"Zone\").alias(\"pickup_zone\"),\n    )\n    return (\n        df_bronze\n            .join(broadcast(df_zones),\n                  df_bronze.PULocationID == df_zones.PULocationID_join,\n                  \"left\")\n            .drop(\"PULocationID_join\")\n    )\n\nprint(\"✓ Fonctions build_bronze, build_silver, build_silver_with_quality définies.\")","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":{"type":"listResults","data":[{"type":"ansi","data":"✓ Fonctions build_bronze, build_silver, build_silver_with_quality définies.\n","name":"stdout","arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[],"metadata":{}}],"arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[],"metadata":{"isDbfsCommandResult":false}},"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":1779197349802,"submitTime":1779197286892,"finishTime":1779197354499,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":[["ansi",76]],"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"2c01a22c-42be-41ce-ac9f-67526cbd2236"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646136,"guid":"9450f654-c975-4d1c-adaf-347948139054","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":13.0,"command":"NB_ITERATIONS = 10\nPAUSE_SECONDS = 20\n\nquality_per_iter = []\n\nfor i in range(NB_ITERATIONS):\n    print(f\"\\n=== Itération {i+1}/{NB_ITERATIONS} ===\")\n\n    # 1. Simulateur chaos\n    sim = TaxiStreamSimulator(\n        output_path=SIM_OUTPUT_PATH,\n        rate=20,\n        interval_seconds=0,\n        mode=\"chaos\",\n        chaos_ratio=0.20,\n        duration_batches=1,\n        seed=200 + i,\n        verbose=False,\n    )\n    t = threading.Thread(target=sim.run, daemon=True)\n    t.start()\n    t.join()\n\n    # 2. Job Bronze\n    q_bronze = (\n        build_bronze_stream().writeStream\n            .format(\"delta\")\n            .outputMode(\"append\")\n            .option(\"checkpointLocation\", CHECKPOINT_BRONZE)\n            .trigger(availableNow=True)\n            .toTable(BRONZE_STREAM_TABLE)\n    )\n    q_bronze.awaitTermination()\n\n    # 3. Job Silver\n    q_silver = (\n        build_silver_stream().writeStream\n            .format(\"delta\")\n            .outputMode(\"append\")\n            .option(\"checkpointLocation\", CHECKPOINT_SILVER)\n            .trigger(availableNow=True)\n            .toTable(SILVER_STREAM_TABLE)\n    )\n    q_silver.awaitTermination()\n\n    # 4. Job Gold (lignes valides)\n    q_gold = (\n        build_silver_with_quality()\n            .filter(col(\"quality_flag\") == \"VALIDE\")\n            .writeStream\n            .format(\"delta\")\n            .outputMode(\"append\")\n            .option(\"checkpointLocation\", CHECKPOINT_GOLD)\n            .trigger(availableNow=True)\n            .toTable(GOLD_STREAM_TABLE)\n    )\n    q_gold.awaitTermination()\n    g_in = (q_gold.lastProgress or {}).get(\"numInputRows\", 0)\n\n    # 5. Job Quarantaine (lignes rejetées)\n    q_qrt = (\n        build_silver_with_quality()\n            .filter(col(\"quality_flag\") != \"VALIDE\")\n            .writeStream\n            .format(\"delta\")\n            .outputMode(\"append\")\n            .option(\"checkpointLocation\", CHECKPOINT_QUARANTINE)\n            .trigger(availableNow=True)\n            .toTable(QUARANTINE_TABLE)\n    )\n    q_qrt.awaitTermination()\n    q_in = (q_qrt.lastProgress or {}).get(\"numInputRows\", 0)\n\n    quality_per_iter.append({\"iter\": i+1, \"gold_inputRows\": g_in, \"qrt_inputRows\": q_in})\n    print(f\"  gold_in={g_in}  quarantine_in={q_in}\")\n\n    if i < NB_ITERATIONS - 1:\n        time.sleep(PAUSE_SECONDS)\n\nprint(\"\\nPipeline S3 terminé.\")","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":{"type":"listResults","data":[{"type":"ansi","data":"\n=== Itération 1/10 ===\n  gold_in=1000  quarantine_in=1000\n\n=== Itération 2/10 ===\n  gold_in=20  quarantine_in=20\n\n=== Itération 3/10 ===\n  gold_in=20  quarantine_in=20\n\n=== Itération 4/10 ===\n  gold_in=20  quarantine_in=20\n\n=== Itération 5/10 ===\n  gold_in=20  quarantine_in=20\n\n=== Itération 6/10 ===\n  gold_in=20  quarantine_in=20\n\n=== Itération 7/10 ===\n  gold_in=20  quarantine_in=20\n\n=== Itération 8/10 ===\n  gold_in=20  quarantine_in=20\n\n=== Itération 9/10 ===\n  gold_in=20  quarantine_in=20\n\n=== Itération 10/10 ===\n  gold_in=20  quarantine_in=20\n\nPipeline S3 terminé.\n","name":"stdout","arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[],"metadata":{}}],"arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[],"metadata":{"isDbfsCommandResult":false}},"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":1779197354527,"submitTime":1779197286894,"finishTime":1779197796845,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":[["ansi",577]],"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"d550fa48-0bcf-4e29-a2e6-c8a507a93316"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646137,"guid":"2cfa2729-27f0-4577-a670-654a10b21e9f","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":14.0,"command":"%md\n## 6. Dashboard qualité — Moment 1 (mi-pipeline)\n\nOn affiche le taux de rejet global et la distribution des types\nd'anomalies à un premier moment, **idéalement à mi-parcours** (en\npratique : juste après la boucle). Le second relevé sera en §7 après le\ntest de résilience.","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":null,"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":null,"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"572f8b17-d7c8-45da-98ba-ad56e3b2f39f"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646138,"guid":"218baaa3-8cae-41ab-a773-36cfdf5f5abd","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":15.0,"command":"from pyspark.sql.functions import count, when, lit\n\ndef quality_dashboard(label):\n    \"\"\"Affiche taux de rejet global + distribution par flag.\"\"\"\n    n_gold = spark.table(GOLD_STREAM_TABLE).count()\n    n_qrt  = spark.table(QUARANTINE_TABLE).count()\n    n_tot  = n_gold + n_qrt\n    rate   = (n_qrt / n_tot * 100) if n_tot else 0\n\n    print(f\"\\n=== Dashboard qualité [{label}] ===\")\n    print(f\"  Lignes valides    : {n_gold:,}\")\n    print(f\"  Lignes rejetées   : {n_qrt:,}\")\n    print(f\"  Total observé     : {n_tot:,}\")\n    print(f\"  Taux de rejet     : {rate:.2f}%  (théorique chaos = 20%)\")\n\n    print(f\"\\n  Distribution par type d'anomalie :\")\n    dist = (\n        spark.table(QUARANTINE_TABLE)\n            .groupBy(\"quality_flag\")\n            .agg(count(\"*\").alias(\"n\"))\n            .orderBy(col(\"n\").desc())\n    )\n    dist.show(truncate=False)\n\n    return {\"label\": label, \"gold\": n_gold, \"quarantine\": n_qrt, \"rate_pct\": round(rate, 2)}\n\nsnapshot_1 = quality_dashboard(\"Moment 1 — fin boucle\")","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":{"type":"listResults","data":[{"type":"ansi","data":"\n=== Dashboard qualité [Moment 1 — fin boucle] ===\n  Lignes valides    : 1,098\n  Lignes rejetées   : 82\n  Total observé     : 1,180\n  Taux de rejet     : 6.95%  (théorique chaos = 20%)\n\n  Distribution par type d'anomalie :\n+--------------------+---+\n|quality_flag        |n  |\n+--------------------+---+\n|ANOMALIE_STATISTIQUE|24 |\n|DISTANCE_NULLE      |16 |\n|LOCATION_NULLE      |16 |\n|DISTANCE_ABERRANTE  |12 |\n|INVERSION_TEMPS     |8  |\n|MONTANT_NEGATIF     |6  |\n+--------------------+---+\n\n","name":"stdout","arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[],"metadata":{}}],"arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[],"metadata":{"isDbfsCommandResult":false}},"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":1779197796886,"submitTime":1779197286906,"finishTime":1779197799149,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":[["ansi",494]],"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"bf61da9c-88f3-4259-b5e8-01067b74b47c"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646139,"guid":"0413173c-d6a1-4e49-80ea-17a7878e02ad","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":16.0,"command":"%md\n## 7. Test de résilience (ÉLIMINATOIRE)\n\n### Mécanisme garanti par Spark + Delta\n\nL'**exactly-once** sur le sink Delta est garanti par 2 verrous :\n\n1. **Le checkpoint** mémorise l'offset lu côté source (table Silver) :\n   `silver_stream_taxi` versions Delta `vN` traitées. Au redémarrage,\n   Spark reprend à `vN+1`, jamais à `vN`.\n2. **L'écriture Delta atomique** : si le cluster crash entre l'écriture\n   des fichiers Parquet et le commit dans `_delta_log`, Delta ignore\n   les fichiers orphelins. Le micro-batch est rejoué proprement, **sans\n   duplication** dans la table cible.\n\n### Test\n\n1. Lire `count(gold_stream_taxi)` avant restart.\n2. Relancer le job Gold avec le **même checkpoint** (simule un crash\n   + redémarrage).\n3. Lire `count(gold_stream_taxi)` après restart.\n4. **Assertion** : counts identiques (aucune ligne dupliquée).","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":null,"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":null,"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"761f1f61-b0f4-4762-8e1f-fedaaa87e9a4"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646140,"guid":"4811bcde-a439-4731-8dd2-40ed3d486c76","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":17.0,"command":"count_before = spark.table(GOLD_STREAM_TABLE).count()\nprint(f\"\uD83D\uDCCA Count Gold AVANT restart : {count_before:,}\")\n\n# Relance forcée du job Gold sur le même checkpoint\n# (équivaut à un restart après crash : Spark consulte le checkpoint,\n# voit que tout a déjà été traité, et n'écrit rien de plus.)\nq_restart = (\n    build_silver_with_quality()\n        .filter(col(\"quality_flag\") == \"VALIDE\")\n        .writeStream\n        .format(\"delta\")\n        .outputMode(\"append\")\n        .option(\"checkpointLocation\", CHECKPOINT_GOLD)\n        .trigger(availableNow=True)\n        .toTable(GOLD_STREAM_TABLE)\n)\nq_restart.awaitTermination()\n\ncount_after = spark.table(GOLD_STREAM_TABLE).count()\nprint(f\"\uD83D\uDCCA Count Gold APRÈS restart : {count_after:,}\")\n\nif count_before == count_after:\n    print(f\"\\n✅ EXACTLY-ONCE VALIDÉ : aucune duplication ({count_before} → {count_after})\")\n    print(\"   Mécanisme : checkpoint Spark (offset Silver) + écriture atomique Delta (_delta_log).\")\nelse:\n    diff = count_after - count_before\n    print(f\"\\n⚠️  DUPLICATION DÉTECTÉE : +{diff} lignes après restart\")","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":{"type":"listResults","data":[{"type":"ansi","data":"\uD83D\uDCCA Count Gold AVANT restart : 1,098\n\uD83D\uDCCA Count Gold APRÈS restart : 1,098\n\n✅ EXACTLY-ONCE VALIDÉ : aucune duplication (1098 → 1098)\n   Mécanisme : checkpoint Spark (offset Silver) + écriture atomique Delta (_delta_log).\n","name":"stdout","arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[],"metadata":{}}],"arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[],"metadata":{"isDbfsCommandResult":false}},"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":1779197799167,"submitTime":1779197286917,"finishTime":1779197802550,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":[["ansi",218]],"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"9d9b5791-793a-4a3e-b319-d3838d37f6a1"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646141,"guid":"aeed47fa-92ed-4663-990f-ac70c074d71c","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":18.0,"command":"%md\n## 8. Dashboard qualité — Moment 2 (post-restart)","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":null,"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":null,"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"e4d97232-bf7a-4fe0-9355-e1bbab05c016"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646142,"guid":"53f9fd4a-f6c6-48cc-be21-4f76a05e2d2c","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":19.0,"command":"snapshot_2 = quality_dashboard(\"Moment 2 — post-restart\")\n\nprint(f\"\\n\uD83D\uDCC8 Évolution entre les 2 relevés :\")\nprint(f\"  Gold : {snapshot_1['gold']} → {snapshot_2['gold']} (Δ={snapshot_2['gold']-snapshot_1['gold']})\")\nprint(f\"  Quarantine : {snapshot_1['quarantine']} → {snapshot_2['quarantine']} (Δ={snapshot_2['quarantine']-snapshot_1['quarantine']})\")\nprint(f\"  Taux rejet : {snapshot_1['rate_pct']}% → {snapshot_2['rate_pct']}%\")\nprint(f\"\\n  Commentaire : si Δ = 0 partout, le restart n'a rien dupliqué (cf §7).\")\nprint(f\"  Le taux de rejet observé doit être proche de 20% (chaos_ratio) si les flags\")\nprint(f\"  couvrent bien toutes les 6 types de corruption injectés.\")","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":{"type":"listResults","data":[{"type":"ansi","data":"\n=== Dashboard qualité [Moment 2 — post-restart] ===\n  Lignes valides    : 1,098\n  Lignes rejetées   : 82\n  Total observé     : 1,180\n  Taux de rejet     : 6.95%  (théorique chaos = 20%)\n\n  Distribution par type d'anomalie :\n+--------------------+---+\n|quality_flag        |n  |\n+--------------------+---+\n|ANOMALIE_STATISTIQUE|24 |\n|DISTANCE_NULLE      |16 |\n|LOCATION_NULLE      |16 |\n|DISTANCE_ABERRANTE  |12 |\n|INVERSION_TEMPS     |8  |\n|MONTANT_NEGATIF     |6  |\n+--------------------+---+\n\n\n\uD83D\uDCC8 Évolution entre les 2 relevés :\n  Gold : 1098 → 1098 (Δ=0)\n  Quarantine : 82 → 82 (Δ=0)\n  Taux rejet : 6.95% → 6.95%\n\n  Commentaire : si Δ = 0 partout, le restart n'a rien dupliqué (cf §7).\n  Le taux de rejet observé doit être proche de 20% (chaos_ratio) si les flags\n  couvrent bien toutes les 6 types de corruption injectés.\n","name":"stdout","arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[],"metadata":{}}],"arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[],"metadata":{"isDbfsCommandResult":false}},"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":1779197802561,"submitTime":1779197286927,"finishTime":1779197804254,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":[["ansi",827]],"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"86c53059-24ff-4666-a245-c69755e0545c"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646143,"guid":"cf71985e-d768-4ed2-a4ad-9314bee27245","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":20.0,"command":"%md\n## 9. Question 1 — Variabilité de `ANOMALIE_STATISTIQUE`\n\n> Le taux de rejet dû à `ANOMALIE_STATISTIQUE` varie fortement d'un\n> micro-batch à l'autre. Proposez une explication. Quel ajustement\n> permettrait de stabiliser ce taux ?\n\n### Explication\n\nDeux causes additives expliquent la variabilité :\n\n1. **Taille d'échantillon faible par batch** : avec `rate=20` trajets\n   par micro-batch et `chaos_ratio=0.20`, on attend ~4 corruptions par\n   batch, soit ~0.67 par type de corruption (6 types). Le simulateur\n   tire chaque corruption **uniformément** (`self._corruptions[int(self.rng.integers(len(self._corruptions)))]`)\n   donc certains batches auront 0 `_huge_amount`, d'autres 2 — la\n   variance est très haute relativement à la moyenne.\n2. **Stats de référence figées** : `ref_borough_stats` est calculée\n   une seule fois (Stream-Static), donc le z-score utilise toujours\n   les mêmes `mean`/`std`. Si un batch tombe sur des trajets\n   \"normaux\" pour le borough X (z-score < 3 mais qui auraient été\n   flagués avec un seuil 2.5), le batch suivant peut tomber sur du\n   `_huge_amount` clair (z-score >> 3). Le taux observé saute.\n\n### Ajustement implémentable\n\nTrois options par ordre de coût croissant :\n\n1. **Augmenter le `rate`** (50-100 trajets/batch) pour réduire la\n   variance par la loi des grands nombres. Limite : RAM Free Edition.\n2. **Lisser sur N batches glissants** : calculer le taux ANOMALIE_STATISTIQUE\n   sur les 5 derniers batches au lieu du dernier seul. Smoothing\n   exponentiel ou moyenne glissante. Implémentation : ajouter\n   un job streaming qui agrège `count(quarantine WHERE flag = 'ANOMALIE_STATISTIQUE')`\n   sur une fenêtre glissante de N×interval, et exposer cette série.\n3. **Recalibrer `ref_borough_stats` périodiquement** (par exemple toutes\n   les heures via un job batch) pour absorber les drifts saisonniers.\n   Ça stabilise les stats à long terme mais pas la variance batch-à-batch.\n\nLa **#2 est la plus efficace** pour le critère \"stabiliser le taux\nobservé\" sans changer la sémantique du flag.","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":null,"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":null,"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"15dac235-87db-4a29-a8b5-effbf36fac83"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646144,"guid":"8599b559-0518-42a2-beca-6bc91176d638","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":21.0,"command":"%md\n## 10. Question 2 — Ignorer définitivement vs réinjecter\n\n> Ignorer définitivement les données en quarantaine ou les réinjecter\n> après correction : quels sont les arguments pour chaque option dans\n> le contexte taxi ? Quelle serait votre décision et pourquoi ?\n\n### Arguments pour **ignorer** (jeter définitivement)\n\n- **Simplicité opérationnelle** : pas de pipeline de correction, pas\n  de table intermédiaire à maintenir. Le coût en code et compute est\n  nul après le routage initial.\n- **Traçabilité préservée** : `quarantine_stream_taxi` reste\n  disponible pour audit, analyse a posteriori, debugging du\n  simulateur ou du capteur amont. Rien n'est physiquement perdu, juste\n  pas réinjecté dans le flux principal.\n- **Évite le biais** : réinjecter des données \"corrigées\" peut masquer\n  un vrai problème système (capteur défaillant, fraude au comptage).\n  Si la flotte rapporte beaucoup de `DISTANCE_NULLE`, c'est un signal\n  métier, pas du bruit à filtrer.\n\n### Arguments pour **réinjecter après correction**\n\n- **Préservation du volume** : 20% de trajets perdus = 20% de revenus\n  non comptabilisés dans les KPI. À l'échelle d'une flotte taxi, c'est\n  massif financièrement.\n- **Corrections évidentes** sont peu risquées :\n  - `MONTANT_NEGATIF` → `abs(total_amount)` si on suppose erreur de\n    signe technique (rare mais existe).\n  - `INVERSION_TEMPS` → permuter `pickup`/`dropoff` si la durée résultante\n    est plausible.\n- **Couverture statistique** : ne pas perdre les trajets longue distance\n  légitimes (course aéroport) qui sont parfois flagués `ANOMALIE_STATISTIQUE`\n  par excès de prudence du z-score.\n\n### Ma décision pour le contexte taxi\n\n**Approche hybride par catégorie** :\n\n| Type | Décision | Raison |\n|---|---|---|\n| `MONTANT_NEGATIF` | **Ignorer** | Signal d'un bug taxi/POS, à investiguer, pas à corriger automatiquement. |\n| `DISTANCE_NULLE` | **Ignorer** | Course annulée ou fraude — à exclure du chiffre d'affaires officiel. |\n| `LOCATION_NULLE` | **Ignorer** | Donnée incomplète, GPS HS — pas réparable a posteriori. |\n| `INVERSION_TEMPS` | **Réinjecter** après correction | Erreur d'horodatage triviale à corriger (permutation). Trajet réel sous-jacent. |\n| `ANOMALIE_STATISTIQUE` | **Réinjecter** avec flag | Probable trajet légitime mais inhabituel (long courrier aéroport, surge nuit). Garder mais signaler dans `gold` avec une colonne `is_outlier`. |\n\nEn pratique on aurait 2 tables Gold : `gold_clean` (sans outliers) et\n`gold_with_outliers` (avec, pour le revenue brut). La quarantaine ne\ncontient au final que les **vraies erreurs techniques**.","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":null,"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":null,"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"47ef5fd9-661b-4960-baf9-77b8d02f38cc"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646145,"guid":"111618c5-77b7-4b4e-b3a3-8f1e7870062b","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":22.0,"command":"%md\n## 11. Arrêt explicite des streams","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":null,"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":null,"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"f97320f9-d61e-4315-814d-51f3dbadd4f4"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":7557603199646146,"guid":"a786d83a-2d72-42f4-accf-6e9ec932ba50","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":23.0,"command":"for q in spark.streams.active:\n    print(f\"Stopping query: {q.name} (id={q.id})\")\n    q.stop()\nprint(\"Toutes les streams sont arrêtées.\")","commandVersion":1,"state":"finished","results":{"type":"listResults","data":[{"type":"ansi","data":"Toutes les streams sont arrêtées.\n","name":"stdout","arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[],"metadata":{}}],"arguments":{},"addedWidgets":{},"removedWidgets":[],"datasetInfos":[],"metadata":{"isDbfsCommandResult":false}},"resultDbfsStatus":"INLINED_IN_TREE","resultDbfsErrorMessage":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"errorDetails":null,"baseErrorDetails":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":1779197804270,"submitTime":1779197286956,"finishTime":1779197804653,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"latestAssumeRoleInfo":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"metadata":{"rowLimit":10000,"byteLimit":2048000},"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultIndex":null,"listResultMetadata":[["ansi",34]],"subcommandOptions":null,"contentSha256Hex":null,"tableResultSettingsMap":{},"nuid":"fbe9e1f8-b9ff-40ea-ae6f-5921699e3f5d"}],"dashboards":[],"guid":"6cbf1058-eb84-4b06-9c31-871497bb6150","globalVars":{},"iPythonMetadata":null,"inputWidgets":{},"notebookMetadata":{"pythonIndentUnit":4},"reposExportFormat":"SOURCE","environmentMetadata":null,"computePreferences":null,"inputWidgetPreferences":null,"environmentSerializationPreferences":null}